Function Reference/comment id fields « WordPress Codex
-----------

Generates two hidden inputs for the comment form to identify the
`comment_post_ID` and `comment_parent` for threaded comments. This tag
must be within the `<form>` section of `comments.php`. New since
WordPress version 2.7.

Usage
-----

`  <?php comment_id_fields(); ?> `

Change Log
----------

Since: 2.7.0

